==English==
===Etymology===
From the Greek '''anekdota''', ''accounts unpublished''; from ''an'', ''not'' + ''ekdota'', ''published accounts''.

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[short]] [[account]] of an [[incident]], often [[humorous]].
# A previously untold, secret account of an incident.
===Derived terms===
[[anecdotal]]

